title: 257. Redefining Men Ft. Jason Wilson
itunes:title: 257. Redefining Men Ft. Jason Wilson
description: In today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined in the studio by the founder & CEO of Yunion, Jason Wilson. They discuss the misconceptions of what it takes to be a real man, how to gain control over your emotions so that you're not a slave to them, and why it's more important now than ever for men to be men.
